data.name: lblInfo.Text
data.value:
Single file export: 1) Click on the ‘Browse’ button to select a PDF file to convert. 2) Choose the necessary options 3) Click on the ‘Export Package’ button and choose a location to save the file/s
Bulk export: 1) Click on ‘Select Files’ and choose all the PDF files 2) Choose the necessary options 3) Click on the ‘Export Packages’ button and choose a folder to save all the packages
